<plot>Every culture has stories and myths that make it unique, but within these stories exists a common thread. This film explores stories that transcend regional cultures to influence humanity as a whole. Utilizing different methods of storytelling, this vignette-style documentary purports that humans are actually bound by such stories and myths, including those that are inherently self-destructive.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?022327</url></doc>
